and that is, in general, you

00:36:20.448 --> 00:36:22.990
could think that the collinear
particles would have some perp

00:36:22.990 --> 00:36:24.070
momentum.

00:36:24.070 --> 00:36:27.650
But we aligned our
axes with the jet axis,

00:36:27.650 --> 00:36:30.190
